# test1000.cns — synthetic test scene, ~1090 nodes with edges
# Five major groups, up to 4 levels deep, with edges suited to each arrangement:
#   • protein_complex   — helix backbone + i→i+3 H-bonds, β-sheet bonds, binding pocket
#   • stellar_neighborhood — orbital rings + star spokes + asteroid belt loop
#   • globular_cluster  — sparse halo constellation + outlier links
#   • crystal_lattice   — hex bonds within unit cells + ionic_bridge linking pivots
#   • nebula_cloud      — sparse filaments

